Lucille Ricksen https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lucille_Ricksen 0 Lucille Ricksen (born Ingeborg Myrtle Elisabeth Ericksen, August 22, 1910 – March 13, 1925) was an American motion picture actress during the silent film era. She died of tuberculosis on March 13, 1925 at the age of 14.
